⠀⠀
As promised here is the FULL TUTORIAL!!!✨
⠀⠀
I’ve been seeing this technique called hydro dipping on Tiktok, Youtube, and here on IG. You can use this technique for many items. I even saw someone dip a iPhone case and it came out really cool✨
⠀⠀⠀
I wanted to make one but of course with a lil Tamara Flare to it. So I added my dazzlers that I always use from Hobby Lobby✨

5 min DIY Glam Candle Holder✨
⠀⠀
This glam candle holder takes 5 min or less to make. Pour in your dazzlers from @hobbylobby. Use hot glue gun to adhere your @dollartree vases. Put a candle in the candle holder. Light it and Bam✨
⠀
Cost $5. Quick easy and anyone can do. These would be great for a wedding, bday gathering, brunch, baby shower, etc. on a budget. You can make several and put them on the table as centerpieces✨
⠀⠀

node.text:
Head to my new closet page @tamarabradshaw_closet to see this full video. Give me a follow!! I’m tryna make it to 30k today!!! Oh and yup I’m chanelling my inner @lilkimthequeenbee and made my type of music video lol✨
⠀⠀
Ok I never give speeches here on IG. But just had a few thoughts as I was sitting here doing some work for social media: 
I was thinking about how my audience on this page is mainly here for Home Decor. But one thing I will say Tamara is always gonna be Tamara. Hahaha ask my friends, I don’t change. Yes I love my Louboutin heels and Chanel bags, and highly obsessed with gorgeous things lol. But who cares. Cause the next minute I’m making Dollartree DIY’s. See I think my audience gets the jist of who I am, and is here for it! Just know I don’t take any of that stuff to serious and I’m very real✨
⠀⠀⠀
BE YOU AND ONLY YOU. I don’t come on this platform ever trying to portray anything other than Who I am. I can be very composed at times,  and the next minute I can be with my friends jumping on a table dancing. Yes and doing videos like this. And I believe my success has to to do with this. Ppl can scope out realness. Don’t come on here acting out a image. It may work for a moment, but that won’t last for long.
⠀
I truly believe if you are true to yourself and put in the real work, you will succeed. You can look at others and learn from them. But copying, NAH. BE YOU AND PUT IN THE WORK. 
⠀⠀⠀
As an entrepreneur ask yourself what is your passion? Mines is Fashion, Home Decor, Dance. So that’s what I’m doing. And I’ve been lucky to be making a living through these platforms and outside of these platforms, in all of these fields. SO YES BE YOU AND PUT IN THE WORK!! As I will continue to do this also. WE GOT GOALS!!! SO LET’S GET IT!!!!!
⠀⠀
DOING ANOTHER BRADSHAW PILLOWCASE RELEASE TOMORROW. SO STAY TUNED✨
⠀⠀

node.text:
One of my fave places to be @cfa_houston!!! Look at all these beauties. If your in Houston stop by boutique. The most gorgeous faux florals and plants periodt! Amazing candles, diffusers and room sprays are available also✨
⠀⠀
CFA Houston
4340 Westheimer Rd. 
Suite 140 
Houston TX 77027✨
⠀⠀⠀⠀
@cfadesigngroup also has locations in Florida. And of course you can shop online. Feel free to DM them or myself if you are interested in anything✨
⠀⠀

node.text:
DIY Hydro Dip Decorative Tray✨
⠀⠀
I got this craftable sign from Michael’s on clearance for like $5. So I decided to turn it into a decorative tray. Same technique called hydro dipping I did on my vase last week. Yes that’s water in the bin. Ad spray paint, mix, and dip. I love it and I will prob cover it with epoxy to give it a more finished look. I will show you if I decide to do that✨
⠀⠀⠀

The Bradshaw Luxury Pillowcase Collection/Marble Edition✨
⠀⠀
Finally another launch is here!!!! Introducing The Bradshaw Marble Collection with @styleupcorp. Bringing you all the glitz and glam that is me!! I’m obsessed with marble print right now, so I designed these beauties with all the details I love in throw pillows. These are perfect to mix and match, and can can be styled with almost any color schemes✨
⠀
Throw pillows take up so much space. So we wanted to make sure we did pillow covers. You can store them, and reuse inserts when it’s time to switch up styles✨
⠀
Each pillow is linked in my stories with some closer up views. You can swipe up and shop. I will also link the inserts I use which are amazing!! Oh and TODAY & TOMORROW only use Code: TAM15 for 15% off my collection. HEAD TO MY STORIES NOW🏃🏽‍♀️✨
